"The left is used to looking for outside aid", for the left "his personal destiny is worth more than Italians. They appeal to external conditioning to try to stop us, only it doesn't work anymore. They tied for the increase of the spread, for the lower wages and the increase of the precarious in order to be able to say that the government failed and it went wrong also there", emphasized the premier, "have tied because it blocked the payment of the Pnrr and they had to surrender" to the data EU "and indeed we have renegotiated it. From the left only lies", he said.&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
And the premier also insisted on the new model of international relations that his government adopted.&nbsp; "We have had international isolation when he ruled the left. The centerpiece has become protagonist" in the world. The comparison is with those who preceded it. "The time of the Giuseppi that changes alliances to the blow of the wind, of the left horobottist is over. Now there is serious Italy, with the right back that defends its national interest that builds peace demonstrating pride," he said.
Nicolas Schmit, who said that the conservatives "are a non-democratic force" came "demonstration, irresponsible. People who to take some votes blow on the fire. You give alibis to extremists to poison the political climate." It is the accusation of Prime Minister Giorgia Meloni at the Fdi kermesse for Europeans in Piazza del Popolo in Rome.
Italy "will no longer go with the saucepan in hand" in Europe, "that season is over, on June 8 and 9 we have the opportunity to archive that season. With the left we will never rule in Italy and Europe, we want to bring the model of the Italian centerpiece in Europe and send to the opposition" the Left, said Meloni, who then spoke of the reforms, returning to turn against 'the left' which is "against the reforms because it wants to continue the palace games", to the left the premier "does not go down, work because the choices of the Italians are worth less. We understood the meaning of the name Democratic Party, it is democracy only if they command them and I do not want to say anything about the 5-star Movement that made decisions on the platforms and now accuses us of authoritarianism" because "we want to give citizens the power" to elect the premier. Thus Giorgia Meloni taking the word on the stage of Piazza del Popolo to the Fdi kermesse for Europeans. "The premier is the mother of all reforms," he observed. And with regard to justice reform, FdI's leader reiterated that&nbsp;"it is right, necessary that we are not afraid to do. Things that don't work must change."
The Committee for the Europeans was also an opportunity to touch themes such as abortion, where the position of Brothers of Italy remains firm. "We want to apply law 194 in its entirety," said Premier.&nbsp; "We do not intend to touch law 194 but apply it in its entirety, even in the part on its prevention because it is true freedom if you can also choose not to abort. If you abort because you have no choice that is not freedom, we add freedom."
<div </div
&nbsp;
Finally the call to vote.&nbsp;"Here we make history and history we can be us. We're at a turning point. It is a referendum" between "the ideological Europe" of the left and "our concrete Europe and fair", said the president of the Council Giorgia Meloni, to the electoral kermesse of Fdi in Piazza del Popolo. "We have shown that our Europe can win," he said, "Europe must not be a superstructure", the left wants to transform Europe "in a monster of bureaucracy that reduces nations to small entities without dignity," said the prime minister. "Europe must rediscover its role in history, take care of few great subjects and let the national states decide on what does not need to be centralized. Otherwise Europe will remain a bureaucratic giant and a political dwarf, and we need the opposite," he said.
